.SH NOTES
The game requires a terminal with color support for the best experience.
Ensure your terminal is at least 80x24 characters to display the game
interface properly.
.PP
When running on a Linux TTY (virtual console), the game uses optimized
screen update routines (erase(), leaveok(), idlok()) to minimize flickering.
For best performance on TTY, ensure framebuffer support is enabled.
